#

Roasted Turkey with Herb Butter

210 min
$45
3500 kcal
Difficulty: 40%
Servings: 10

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-FreePaleo

Cuisine:

AmericanTraditional

Course:

Main CourseHoliday Meal

Tags:

Main CourseThanksgivingHoliday Meal

Description

Juicy turkey infused with aromatic herb butter for a delicious holiday feast.

Ingredients

  • whole turkey: 12-14 lbs
  • unsalted butter: 1 cup
  • fresh rosemary: 2 tablespoons
  • fresh thyme: 2 tablespoons
  • fresh sage: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic: 4 cloves
  • salt: 2 tablespoons
  • black pepper: 1 tablespoon
  • lemon: 1
  • onion: 1 large
  • carrots: 2
  • celery: 2
